  "_comment": "kol simple-bar settings — symlink to ~/.simplebarrc (bootstrap). simple-bar ALSO writes settings to localStorage via its own panel (cmd+click the bar); this file seeds/overrides it. After tuning in the panel, copy the exported JSON back here so the repo stays truth. Reference look: naked bar —  + app pill left, ONE capsule right, wallpaper between (refs 13-16 in _tmp/kol-terminality-refs).",
